# Reference material and internal trackers — kept locally, not redistributed.
# FM 1-02.2 is a US Government work (public domain in the US), but the PDF is
# 10.5 MB and that status does not travel internationally. The extracted
# docs/FM_1-02.2.txt stays tracked: it is greppable and the ai/ docs cite it.
docs/*.pdf
docs/*.xlsx

# Python bytecode (from scripts/*.py)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
